plot: Jeana's son Colton breaks his hand in a fight about drugs, Kimberly and her family hire a 'dog guru' to deal with their out-of-control dog and Jo is struggling to keep up with her responsibilities around the house. Vicki interrupts Briana's date fearing her daughter is too serious with her boyfriend, Colby, and Vicki and Lauri's attempt at after-work cocktails in the Jacuzzi is crashed by Michael and his friends, who are all smitten with Lauri.—Anonymous
